It simply means managing and controlling the configurations of each microservice in the system

What does configuration actually means ?

Configuration means or Configurations refers to the parameters that control the behaviour of your application or the service
And Configuration may include details such as database connections , external service urls , caching systems and more .

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

How does spring boot loads configuration

1. Parsing and Environment -> parsing application.properties or application.yml file and added to the environment which is required to run an application
2. Relaxed Binding -> It will bind the value to the key, and here key is in application.properties or application.yml file




